xplainer-northkorea__wrapper .content-wrapper .cards .card.comment{background-color:#efefec;border-top:1px solid #e6711b}.explainer-northkorea__wrapper .content-wrapper .cards .card.comment h4,.explainer-northkorea__wrapper .content-wrapper .cards .card.comment.big h4{color:#333}.explainer-northkorea__wrapper .content-wrapper .cards .card.comment.byline{color:#e6711b}.explainer-northkorea__wrapper .content-wrapper .cards .card.comment:focus,.explainer-northkorea__wrapper .content-wrapper .cards .card.comment:hover{background:#e3e3de}@media all and (min-width:46.25em){.explainer-northkorea__wrapper .content-wrapper .cards .card img+h4{max-width:calc(100%);margin-top:-4px}#explainerwrapper{width:740px;overflow:hidden}#explainercontent{width:460px;float:left;margin-left:20px;border-right:1px solid #dfdfdf;padding-right:9px;margin-right:10px}}@media all and (min-width:61.25em){#explainerwrapper{width:980px}#explainercontent{width:620px}}@media all and (min-width:71.25em){#explainerwrapper{width:1140px}#explainertitle{width:140px;float:left}#explainercontent{width:620px;margin-left:0;margin-top:9px}#explainercards{width:300px;margin-top:9px}}@media all and (min-width:81.25em){#explainerwrapper{width:1300px}#explainertitle{width:220px}}</style><h1 class='header'>North Korea</h1>\n<div class='content-wrapper' id='explainerwrapper'>\n  <div class='container-title' id='explainertitle'>North Korea's nuclear progress in 2017</div>\n  <div class='explainer' id='explainercontent'>\n    <div class='chapter'>\n      <img src=\"https://interactive.guim.co.uk/thrashers/explainer-northkorea/hashed/northkorea_sq01.67643b79.jpg\">\n      <h3><span class='title'>Missiles</span></h3>\n      <p>North Korea’s efforts to develop a nuclear-armed intercontinental ballistic missile capable of hitting the US mainland have accelerated with a series of successful missile tests, including North Korea’s first launch of an ICBM on 4 July.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class='chapter'>\n      <h3><span class='title'>Targeting the US</span></h3>\n      <p>The potential range of the Hwasong-14 tested on 28 July includes the continental US. Observers noted the missile had been quickly modified from its previous test on 4 July – a strong indicator of the regime’s enhanced capabilities.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class='chapter'>\n      <h3><span class='title'>Nuclear tests</span></h3>\n      <p>North Korea needs to produce a miniaturised nuclear bomb that can be loaded on to an ICBM to complete a credible weapon. An underground test on 3 September suggested that milestone may be within reach.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class='feedback' data-explainer-name='north-korea'>\n      <div class='label'>Was this helpful?</div>\n      <button data-link-name='tag page explainer : like' class=\"feedback-button button like\" value=\"like\" aria-label=\"Yes\">\n          <span>\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 40 40\">\n              <path fill=\"#ffffff\" d=\"M33.78 22.437l-4.228 13.98L27.93 37.5 5.062 34.14V15.503l7.8-1.517L24.354 2.5h1.624L28.9 5.426l-4.548 8.67h.107l10.477 1.31\"></path>\n            </svg>\n          </span>\n      </button>\n      <button data-link-name='tag page explainer : like' class=\"feedback-button button dislike\" value=\"dislike\" aria-label=\"No\">\n          <span>\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 40 40\">\n              <path fill=\"#ffffff\" d=\"M33.78 22.437l-4.228 13.98L27.93 37.5 5.062 34.14V15.503l7.8-1.517L24.354 2.5h1.624L28.9 5.426l-4.548 8.67h.107l10.477 1.31\"></path>\n            </svg>\n          </span>\n      </button>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"feedback-thankyou\" hidden=\"\" aria-role=\"alert\" aria-live=\"polite\">\n        <div class='label'>Thank you for your feedback</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class='cards' id='explainercards'>\n    <div class='card big news'>\n      <a data-link-name='story-north-korea' href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/sep/12/north-korea-sanctions-un-security-council-unanimously-agrees-new-measures'>North Korea sanctions: UN security council unanimously agrees new measures</a>\n      <img src=\"https://interactive.guim.co.uk/thrashers/explainer-northkorea/hashed/nk_sanctions.4fe55a2e.jpg\">\n      <h4>North Korea sanctions: UN security council unanimously agrees new measures</h4>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class='card small news'>\n      <a data-link-name='story-north-korea' href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/aug/30/north-koreas-kim-jong-un-says-missile-launch-a-prelude-to-containing-guam'>Donald Trump says 'talking not the answer' to North Korea crisis</a>\n      <h4>Donald Trump says 'talking not the answer' to North Korea crisis</h4>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class='card small comment'>\n      <a data-link-name='story-north-korea' href='https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2017/aug/29/north-korea-missiles-fire-fury-japan-delegitimise-kim-jong-un'>North Korea’s missiles can be stopped – but not by ‘fire and fury’</a>\n      <h4><span class=\"inline-quote\"><svg width=\"19\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 33 20\"><path d=\"M9.002 20c3.85.068 6.932-3.104 7-6.994.068-3.892-3.15-6.937-7-7.006-2.016-.036-3.59.694-4.888 2.053A9.968 9.968 0 0 1 4.001 6.5C4.064 2.97 7.414.937 11.003 1l-1-1C3.98 0 .098 4.447.002 10.006c-.097 5.557 3.35 9.892 9 9.994zm17 0c3.85.068 6.932-3.104 7-6.994.068-3.892-3.15-6.937-7-7.006-2.016-.036-3.59.694-4.888 2.053a9.968 9.968 0 0 1-.113-1.553c.063-3.53 3.413-5.563 7.002-5.5l-1-1c-6.022 0-9.904 4.447-10 10.006-.097 5.557 3.35 9.892 9 9.994z\"></path></svg></span>\n        North Korea’s missiles can be stopped – but not by ‘fire and fury’<br /><span class='byline'>John Nilsson-Wright</span></h4>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <img\n    style=\"height:0;width:0;visibility:hidden;position:absolute;z-index: 1;\"\n    height=\"0\"\n    width=\"0\"\n    src=\"https://interactive.guim.co.uk/thrashers/explainer-northkorea/hashed/empty.5ef2ef64.gif\"\n    onload=\"var script=document.createElement('script');script.src='https://interactive.guim.co.uk/thrashers/explainer-northkorea/hashed/main.5596de3f.js'; document.body.appendChild(script);\"\n  />\n\n\n</div>\n</div>",
